# AI Rules for elonehoo.me

## Code Style
- Follow the existing code style in the project
- Use TypeScript for new code
- Use Vue 3 Composition API
- Maintain consistency with existing components

## Project Structure
- VitePress files are in src/vitepress/
- Theme components are in theme/
- Content is in content/
- Static assets are in content/public/

## Development Guidelines
- Always explain changes before implementing
- Prefer small, focused changes
- Test changes locally before suggesting
- Respect existing conventions

## Communication
- Be concise and clear
- Provide context when suggesting changes
- Ask for clarification when unsure
- Explain technical concepts simply

## Tools
- Use pnpm for package management
- Follow linting rules in eslint.config.js
- Use VitePress for documentation
